column6: dissolves in a puddle@of thick smelly ooze.
dies his face frozen in@an expression of shock and disbelief
fades away exclaiming I'm free! Art thou The One?
gasps:@"What you sow you shall reap!"
dies with@a sneer on his face
sputters around a bit@and then explodes
disappears in a@puff of greasy black smoke
goes up@in a cloud of smoke
is consumed@in a fiery orange ball
crumbles into a@heap of shattered bones
dissolves in@a thick vile cloud of gas
is consumed in a@sulphurous cloud of smoke
falls to the@ground in a crumpled heap
melts into a puddle@of bubbling goo
appears human for an@instant and then expires
is consumed in a@huge red cloud of smoke
